<script type="text/javascript">


    function auto_busqueda() {
        console.log("funciono")
        var texto = document.getElementById("terminoBusqueda").value;
        var href = "https://www.bancolombia.com/acerca-de/buscador?termino=" + texto;
        window.location.href = (href)
    }

    function auto_busqueda_movil() {
        console.log("funciono")
        var texto = document.getElementById("terminibusquedamovil").value;
        var href = "https://www.bancolombia.com/acerca-de/buscador?termino=" + texto;
        window.location.href = (href)
    }

    $(function () {
        function split(valor) {
            return valor.split(/,\s*/);
        }
        function extractLast(termino) {
            var t = split(termino).pop();
            return t;
        }

        $("#terminoBusqueda")
            // don't navigate away from the field on tab when selecting an item
            .bind(
                "keydown",
                function (event) {

                    if (event.keyCode === $.ui.keyCode.TAB
                        && $(this).autocomplete("instance").menu.active) {
                        event.preventDefault();
                    }
                })
            .autocomplete({
                source: function (request, response) {

                    $
                        .getJSON(
                            "/autocompletarBusqueda/rest/servicio/consultarSugerenciasPorClave",
                            {
                                term: extractLast(request.term),
                                claveBusqueda: extractLast(request.term)
                            }, response);
                },
                search: function () {

                    var term = extractLast(this.value);
                    if (term.length < 2) {
                        return false;
                    }
                },
                focus: function () {
                    // prevent value inserted on focus
                    return false;
                },
                select: function (event, ui) {

                    var terms = split(this.value);
                    // remove the current input
                    terms.pop();
                    // add the selected item
                    terms.push(ui.item.value);
                    // add placeholder to get the comma-and-space at the end
                    terms.push("");
                    this.value = terms.join("");
                    return false;
                }
            });
    });
</script>
